<Layout
	title="Press Bio"
	description="Press bio for Pieter de Jong"
>
	<div class="content-container">
		<div class="press-content">
			<h2>Bio for Press Use</h2>
			<p class="press-bio">
				Pieter de Jong is a Senior Software Engineer with over 7 years of experience in consumer finance, e-commerce, digital agriculture, and solar energy. Starting his career in Silicon Valley after immigrating from Amsterdam, he has worked across the full spectrum of company stages, from seed-stage startups to public companies. His expertise spans full-stack web development, data pipelines, and applied mathematics, with a particular interest in machine learning. Currently pursuing a part-time MSc in Computer Science at Georgia Tech, Pieter combines technical depth with a passion for building impactful products. He has lived and worked in major tech hubs including Miami, NYC, San Francisco, and Silicon Valley, bringing a global perspective to his engineering work.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>

